From a6dbd2708ee4cd3676988534b6bc8e6aae5ab814 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: zhidao su <suzhidao@xiaomi.com>
Date: Tue, 3 Mar 2026 14:09:58 +0800
Subject: [PATCH 29/69] sched_ext: Use READ_ONCE() for plain reads of
 scx_watchdog_timeout

scx_watchdog_timeout is written with WRITE_ONCE() in scx_enable():

    WRITE_ONCE(scx_watchdog_timeout, timeout);

