From 0a82f4bd8c94ec44565c2bb87875da414792fc47 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Tejun Heo <tj@kernel.org>
Date: Wed, 4 Mar 2026 11:26:48 -1000
Subject: [PATCH 62/69] sched_ext: Convert scx_dump_state() spinlock to raw
